Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我说的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...你叫什么名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,请求许可...
