Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,拉格...纳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,拉...格纳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:10:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,拉格...纳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,拉...格...纳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,拉格纳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不会请你吃饭哦
